694
00:59:05.000 --> 00:59:08.375
Don't worry. It's my job
to get Dad's keys back. See you later.

695
00:59:16.125 --> 00:59:17.667
Whoa.

696
00:59:17.750 --> 00:59:20.917
Look how high it got.
Come on. Let's go.

697
00:59:25.750 --> 00:59:28.958
"Get your head out of the clouds, boy.
Draw me some money.

